sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / API Client
    participant Hub as Hub Control Plane
    participant Queue as Hub Task Queue
    participant Planner as Planning Service
    participant Store as Goal/Plan Storage

    User->>Hub: Submit Goal (minimal payload)
    Hub->>Store: Persist Goal + trace_id
    Hub->>Queue: Enqueue planning task
    Queue->>Planner: Deliver planning request
    Planner->>Planner: Build bounded plan graph
    Planner-->>Hub: Plan draft + policy hints
    Hub->>Store: Persist Plan + plan nodes
    Hub-->>User: Goal accepted + plan summary
